channel.title: Fire Emblem Fates FM - Pre-ins - Filled!
channel.description:
_You are the ocean’s gray waves, destined to seek_ _life beyond the shore just out of reach_ _Yet the waters ever change, flowing like time_ **_The path is yours to climb_** ![image|690x365](upload://r8affqIGZwDIZaYJ1qBWyg1NF8w.jpg) Hosted by @Icibalus and @Marluxion
- 34 players, making this the largest game ever played on the site! - Lots of flavor on rolecards, fun mechanics, events and abilites. - Rolemadness - Everyone gets an ability of some kind! - In-Thread Attacks - ITAs are back, and with more death than ever! This will make the game fast, chaotic and a furious test of skill. - **Explicitly Non-Bastard** **10 pre-in slots will be avaliable. The game proper will start on the 26th of July, so make sure that you can be avaliable then. Please join this game, as I promise it will be a huge amount of fun!** **Full signups will open a few days before the start date.** 1. htm 2. Firekitten 3. Livicus 4. Mthejoker 5. Celeste_Ludenberg 6. Hippolytus 7. Tw1light 8. Sam17z 9. Whammerist 10. MaximusPrime 11. PoisonedSquid 12. Vulgard 13. Simon 14. orangeandblack5 15. Insanity 16. Shurian 17. Damafaud 18. Boss110 19. Eevee ----- *PS: if you have any questions, just ask us and we'll tell you what we can.*
